AlcesActAsDictionary
====================

This is a simple plugin to add functions to use a model as a dictionary is in the biorails systems.
It adds the following class methods :-

  lookup(name) First Matching item 
  like(name) List of matching instances default limited to 20

Then to the object the to_s is changed to return the 'name'



Example
=======

class DataSystem < ActiveRecord::Base

  acts_as_dictionary :name

end


